summary: This document is a certificate from the Department of Transportation certifying the authenticity of records related to a specific aircraft, Dieing 727-31, including its serial number and registration details. It includes signatures from officials confirming their roles and the validity of the records.

persons.name: Michelle Endsley
persons.context: Michelle Endsley is identified as the legal custodian of the aircraft records and signed the certificate of true copy.

persons.name: Kevin All
persons.context: Kevin All is mentioned as the acting manager who affixed the seal of the Department of Transportation to the certificate.

keyFacts: The document certifies the authenticity of records pertaining to the aircraft Dieing 727-31.
The aircraft's serial number is 20115 and it was formerly registered as N9083E.
The certificate was signed on August 23, 2021.
Michelle Endsley is the legal custodian of the records.
Kevin All is the acting manager who confirmed the certificate.
